{"text": "Eu nem sou muito fã de jogo de luta mas eu tenho que admitir que esse jogo é incrível. A história é muito legal, é em torno de umas 5 horas e eu acho que tá no tamanho perfeito. Parece um filme. Eu sou bem casual em termos de games de luta mas achei fácil fazer uns combos legais com os diversos personagens diferentes que tem no jogo, cada um com sua peculiaridade e são todos muito bem feitos mesmo. Eu adorei as intros em que os personagens conversam entre si. Se até eu consegui emendar uns combos aqui e ali, significa que foi bem divertido e é bem acessível para todos os jogadores, ainda mantendo um bom level de maestria pra quem é mais hardcore. Excelente jogo, recomendo pra todos.", "appid": "627270", "steamid": "profiles/76561198079173277", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1605528000.0}
{"text": "I bought this game on DVD many years ago. So it was my second complete play after long time. - not very long (if you dont search for the suit cases, no speed runs, no time trail, the single player is fast done) -no Steam Achievements (other ports has achievements) -interesting character that come to short -sometimes it feel a bit to much the same -no real (end) boss fight + added 7 Trading Cards after 11 years + interesting  level design (not always, could be more details/ designs but its from 2009) + good story (not epic but fine) + fair price or very good price with discount for this 5 hours of gameplay + a few nice extra developer screens + feels like Splinter Cell, Prince of Persia, Assassins Creed but with less fighting, less stealth, in a different world, fast pace without boring tower climbs or hide for long + even on easy a bit challening (on normal & hard sure a challenge) I love this game & i am happy to play it again. Twice with Dice and i dont regret it. Its still a very good game even without top graphics, it has is charme. Cant wait to start Nr. 2 Catalyst :) I hope U enjoy it like me. + not to much Parcour, some fights vs different enemies", "appid": "17410", "steamid": "profiles/76561197973230221", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "23", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1591704000.0}
