{"text": "From beginning to end I felt as if I went to a place where I met a lovely lady who welcomed me to have a conversation about her past. A past so intense with danger, trauma, and pain. My first reaction was how nice it was to listen to her telling the story. How clear her voice was that it made me feel rather relaxed and hanging on every word. She recalled her memories not with anger or tears, but rather there was a calm. I don't know her, but after finishing the game a little part of her stayed with me. I admire her courage and strength. Some people will play this \"game\" and just see a game. Others like me will see a person who, with her family, went through so much suffering. She is an example of what it is to survive terrible times in life. I thank the developer and her for sharing the story with us.", "appid": "1073900", "steamid": "profiles/76561198287952411", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "13", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1573473600.0}
