{"text": "DEMONIACA Everlasting Night is a gothic hardcore RPG game. In the story, we will play for a young girl whose family and friends were killed by demons. She herself, was seriously injured, but by a miracle she survived and now burning with desire for revenge. We have a large map of the Tower of Babel, which is divided into many sublevels. To move from one sublevel to another, you need to unlock a special ability, which can be obtained only after defeating the local boss. During the passage you can highlight several features, first, this game is extremely hardcore, it is displayed in many aspects. For example, the enemies hit hard and do not know mercy, the traps are set so that the slightest mistake can be the last and lead to death, accidentally encountered mini boss, can kill with a single blow and in general the design of levels is made so as to inflict the player as much suffering in passing. It can be noted that there is no autosaves and checkpoints in the game, only manual save at special portals. We couldn't get to it, we lose all our loot and experience and try again. The second feature of the game is the RPG elements. For killing enemies, we get the experience, through which we improve our level and get the opportunity to pump the skills of your hero, such as strength, agility, endurance. In addition, we can improve the characteristics of the character, through certain items that will fall out of the destroyed crates and chests, killed enemies and bosses. The third feature is a combat system based on combo strikes, which will be used frequently in the future, so it is strongly recommended to use a gamepad. I would like to note the atmosphere in the game, in which a very cool and dynamic soundtrack and beautiful Pixel-Art design levels in black and red tones.", "appid": "1107370", "steamid": "profiles/76561198117800332", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "3", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1602504000.0}
