{"text": "Great idle game, with all kinds of upgrades, and an upgradable, programmable automation system, plus THREE tiers of Prestiging. You play apparently the rear gunner of a transport, and you can beef up your aimable turret, or buy sub-turrets that automatically pick targets and fire. Some of the weapons are expected, like the fighter/bomber bays, others are quite creative like the Nyan Cat. And EVERYTHING is upgradeable. Your first Prestige, you get a little Drone that helps you not just with extra damage, but also add-ons that boost your stats that you can't have on the main ship! Once you max out all the features, there's another tier of Prestige, that increases the limits and cargo price of the features, so you can upgrade them STILL further! Graphics look like a self-playing Galaga or something similar. sound is minimalistic (I turned it off quickly). All in all, everything one should want in an idle game!", "appid": "685310", "steamid": "profiles/76561197971951603", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1573732800.0}
