{"text": "Well actually, i've completed this series already (till part 3). Though it was a pirated version i downloaded from torrent (shame i know) because i didn't expect much from this Grisaia \"sequel-ish\" series and don't want to spend my bucks for \"unpromising\" vn (sorry FrontWing :D). But they turn out to be a reaaally amazing ride. The stories, arts, musics, and voice acting are 5/5. This urges me to purchase all the retail version (part 1 to 4) to support the developer. Front Wing really deserves all the bucks for this quality. If you're a real fan of Grisaia franchise, you should buy this series. Now i'm on my way to finish this vn for the 2nd time cause part 4 is out baby~. On volume 1, the story circles around Arisaka Shiori a new homeroom teacher for Mihama Academy and the people on the academy in general. The only cons for me on this vn series is that it is really short IMO. You can even complete this part 1 in few hours.", "appid": "606510", "steamid": "profiles/76561198042495360", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1517400000.0}
