{"text": "While nice to see more \"Facebook\" style farming games being brought to Steam, My Little Farmies falls short of a fun experience. I disagree with some of the reviewers labeling this as a P2W game - there is nothing separating this from a Farmville-esque experience, where you certainly are able to play F2P without sacrificing much in terms of fun. The issue that comes with this is that there is no seamless integration of social media lists to add friends. It is significantly more difficult to \"ask a friend for help\" in-game relying solely on the Steam client or an email-based friend system. Steamworks integration is low - there are no achievements or trading cards. While these aren't massive issues, almost every game has these as a feature. Another recent F2P Steam release I've played, Harvest Seasons, even connects rewards, like an in-game currency to achievements, a great way to retain players. Control interface is very annoying, the most frustrating being the ability to rotate only after placing an object, and only being able to do it one at a time and then having to click>rotate>click for each item is monotonous and shows the blemishes of this game compared to veteran offerings in the same genre. I don't think My Little Farmies is a bad game, but it certainly doesn't stand out among the offerings of Zynga, and absolutely doesn't hold itself against any good mobile farming/idle sim genre offering. So while this is an okay F2P experience on Steam, which is heavily lacking in any good Zynga-esque farming simulators, it doesn't change the fact that it's not a good overall experience in comparison to what is available on PC through Facebook games/Zynga. Since the game has almost no Steamworks integration already, it's almost pointless to argue that it's just not better to play another, more superior game from this genre on PC through a non-Steam outlet.", "appid": "789100", "steamid": "profiles/76561198038056805", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "17", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1520164800.0}
